{"tid":927472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又贏！垃圾徵費：環保團體建議政府向綜援戶等提供補貼","createTime":"2018-12-04T07:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T03:55:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8f1f5225bb3728f99e243170c31deefe492dc3","tid":927472,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:38:17.000Z","msg":"政府計劃最快在2020年底落實垃圾徵費，5個環保團體綠領行動、綠色力量、綠惜地球、長春社及綠色和平，委託樹仁大學就市民對垃圾徵費立法取態進行調查，發現無論公屋住戶或私人樓宇住戶均支持實施垃圾徵費，大多受訪者亦支持「污者自付」原則處理垃圾。<span style=\"color: red;\">環團建議政府向綜援戶等提供補貼，</span>料可進一步釋除經濟負擔的疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181204/bkn-20181204131900411-1204_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181204%2Fbkn-20181204131900411-1204_00822_001.html&d=AtWwe%2FdLOZlZPdCPsK%2F9a0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=ed4272a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181204/bkn-20181204131900411-1204_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"dc51fdd47a033edaff8cd30d921adfde0c1f4636","tid":927472,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/133811_1d9fcb4f63a440a77c32deb42756910e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F133811_1d9fcb4f63a440a77c32deb42756910e.png&h=529146e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"092f45220641b8e706c5cab2befa1cedb275d10f","tid":927472,"uid":161945,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"果班人本身已經係垃圾"},{"pid":"4da785c63be19dd9847db6716ac8909a4f9046b4","tid":927472,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"092f45220641b8e706c5cab2befa1cedb275d10f","tid":927472,"uid":161945,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:41:22.000Z","msg":"果班人本身已經係垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"負負得正<br 